blocks.saveContent: Our experts from FLS Logistics and FLS Warehousing enjoyed a special time networking at AerOceaNetwork Annual General Meeting 2022. As the Platinum Sponsor of the event, we welcomed worldwide industry leaders and AON members to discuss the latest developments of our industry and our expanding FLS Group.

blocks.saveContent: Following the successful XLP AGM 2022 and AON AGM 2022 events, we kickstarted the beginning of the networking season, as well as great partnerships and business opportunities. We are looking forward to more in the near future.
